      "name": "Pump pressure-head validation across operating envelope",
      "description": "Simulated pressure head (ΔP) compared against manufacturer-supplied hydraulic performance curves at five operating points spanning 2–6 L/min and 2000–3500 RPM. Mean absolute error 3.2%, within the 5% acceptance band. Grid-converged results used (GCI < 1% on ΔP)."
    },
