      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; sample size and biological variability documented.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis experiments conducted with n=3 independent blood samples per operating point (15 total test runs). Inter-sample coefficient of variation in RH index ranged 6–11%. Sample size justification documented in experimental protocol EP-2023-07. Formal statistical power analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
