      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions derived directly from experimental test protocol measurements. Fluid density and viscosity matched to within 2% of experimental measurements at 37 °C. Pump geometry in simulation derived from CMM-verified CAD model with dimensional tolerances ± 0.05 mm. Equivalency documented in simulation-experiment traceability matrix (TM-2023-11). Gradation 1 accepted at MRL 2."
    }
